20
00:01:29,140 --> 00:01:31,560
[Legend of Fuyao]

21
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:34,340
~ Episode 14 ~

22
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:41,680
That's strange.

23
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:45,370
Uncle Zhou clearly said this Five-Colored Stone is to unlock the seal.

24
00:01:45,370 --> 00:01:47,760
Could it be that this place has something to do with the seal?

25
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:00,720
Stop!

26
00:02:02,310 --> 00:02:04,900
Miss, why do you walk here?

27
00:02:08,830 --> 00:02:10,280
It's good that you are here.

28
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,520
I just got lost!

29
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,380
Can you tell me how to go back?

30
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:16,610
This is a restricted area in the manor.

31
00:02:17,490 --> 00:02:19,290
Restricted area?

32
00:02:21,170 --> 00:02:23,240
I just came into the manor in less than two days.

33
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,940
I can't tell the directions.

34
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:27,340
Let me tell you. Butler Wei has said that

35
00:02:27,340 --> 00:02:30,850
whoever gets inside the courtyard behind this door will get himself killed.

36
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:33,990
Since you are new here, I'll just let it go this time.

37
00:02:33,990 --> 00:02:35,420
From now on, just be careful.

38
00:02:35,420 --> 00:02:37,070
Get out of here quickly!

39
00:02:38,290 --> 00:02:39,960
Thank you!

40
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,630
What did you say?

41
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:54,620
News from the palace.

42
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:58,340
They are saying that the king is recuperating well daily.

43
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,200
Looks like...

44
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:17,400
it's time to ask Medical Sage Zong for help.

45
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,840
Yes!

46
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:32,450
Why did you stay lighted up during the day?

47
00:03:32,450 --> 00:03:35,700
Why do I have to unlock this annoying seal?

48
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:37,470
And who am I?

49
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:43,680
[Heavenly Peace Gate]

50
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,770
My respectful Prime Minister.

51
00:03:55,770 --> 00:03:57,770
How is the king?

52
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:09,160
After the ceremony of bestowing the title on Heir Apparent,

53
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:12,060
Marquis Zhang intensified the palace security.

54
00:04:12,060 --> 00:04:14,970
The king is being guarded tightly.

55
00:04:14,970 --> 00:04:16,910
Not mention that no commoner can get close,

56
00:04:16,910 --> 00:04:22,560
even all the medicine and meals that were sent in were all tested very carefully.

57
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:28,160
Marquis Zhang is so dedicated.

58
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:32,720
He even used the poison testing method that no one has used for hundreds of years.

59
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,930
Great attention was given to the entire process.

60
00:04:34,930 --> 00:04:37,920
Even something as small as a needle can't be inserted.

61
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:41,400
This Marquis Gentle Bright really sees himself as the pillar of the nation

62
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,730
and the king's right-hand man of Deep Water.

63
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:47,990
I have invited Zong Yue, Medical Sage Zong.

64
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:51,360
Medical Sage Zong's skill is superb.

65
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:55,240
I'm sure he can revive the king's spirit.

66
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:58,760
Thank you, Prime Minister, for your effort.

67
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:02,540
But right now is a critical time.

68
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:07,690
I'm afraid that I can only let Medical Sage to go in alone to treat the king.

69
00:05:07,690 --> 00:05:10,890
I hope Prime Minister can understand.

70
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:14,690
Okay. Let me go in to notify the king.

71
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:25,840
Treating the king is a matter of extreme importance.

72
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:30,090
There's something that I need to clarify with you.

73
00:05:30,090 --> 00:05:32,030
Please say it, Medical Sage Zong.

74
00:05:32,030 --> 00:05:38,690
I'm not sure whether Prime Minister wants the king to live or die tonight.

75
00:06:52,590 --> 00:06:53,880
How come you are here?

76
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:56,430
- Am I that easy to recognize?
- Yes.

77
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:58,310
What are you here for?

78
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,780
I—

79
00:07:02,550 --> 00:07:04,460
I'm here to look for the Earth Absorbing Bell.

80
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:08,270
Let me show you a place. Let's go.

81
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:19,570
The Earth Absorbing Bell should be in there.

82
00:07:20,150 --> 00:07:23,130
Could it be that stone of yours is able to sense the Earth Absorbing Bell?

83
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:26,400
Yes, if my speculation is correct.

84
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:31,700
It's just that I don't understand. In the past when the Five-Colored Stone was in contact with the Earth Absorbing Bell,

85
00:07:31,700 --> 00:07:33,540
there was no such reaction.

86
00:07:34,870 --> 00:07:37,460
Then there's only one explanation.

87
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:40,160
The Earth Absorbing Bell is being confined in here.

88
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:42,560
So the Earth Absorbing Bell knows how to call for help.

89
00:08:03,410 --> 00:08:05,350
Let me do it!

90
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:38,960
Could it be?

91
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,560
Zhan Beiye,

92
00:08:41,770 --> 00:08:43,500
I have another method.

93
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:30,730
Who sent you here?

94
00:09:30,730 --> 00:09:33,390
It's Qi Zhen again.

95
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:39,970
Don't forget that Deep Water is mine.

96
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:50,400
I can give you wealth and honor.

97
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:54,080
I can give you whatever you want.

98
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:05,880
Why do you look so much alike?

99
00:10:07,030 --> 00:10:11,310
Whom does my face let you recall?

100
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:18,170
Wenyi of the Xuanyuan royal clan back then.

101
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:26,390
You are not fit to mention this title.

102
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:33,100
Fifteen years already,

103
00:10:33,810 --> 00:10:38,230
everything in this palace stays exactly the same.

104
00:10:40,010 --> 00:10:42,800
It still has no regard for people's feelings.

105
00:10:44,530 --> 00:10:47,240
You are still alive.

106
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:55,440
You are not dead yet,

107
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:58,470
then how can I die before you?

108
00:10:58,470 --> 00:11:00,660
Do you want to kill me?

109
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:12,240
The offspring of Heir Apparent Wenyi...

110
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:15,900
will take back everything!

111
00:11:57,260 --> 00:11:59,050
What sound is that?

112
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:05,780
It’s the Earth Absorbing Bell.

113
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:12,550
Follow me.

114
00:12:48,980 --> 00:12:51,030
Indeed, it’s here.

115
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:08,030
Since the Earth Absorbing Bell is here, Xiaoqi will definitely be here as well.

116
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,950
Don’t be careless.

117
00:13:09,950 --> 00:13:12,010
Xiaoqi may not be here.

118
00:13:12,010 --> 00:13:13,420
Why?

119
00:13:13,420 --> 00:13:18,120
If the Earth Absorbing Bell was with Xiaoqi, Xiaoqi’s body would corrode,

120
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:20,490
but it’s not life-threatening now.

121
00:13:20,490 --> 00:13:24,410
But if you suddenly remove its connection with Xiaoqi,

122
00:13:24,410 --> 00:13:26,530
he will be in danger instead.

123
00:13:26,530 --> 00:13:28,590
What are you waiting for? Take the bell and go save him.

124
00:13:28,590 --> 00:13:29,980
Wait a minute.

125
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:34,630
This Earth Absorbing Bell is magical yet evil.

126
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:36,310
Others cannot just touch it.

127
00:13:36,310 --> 00:13:40,670
Only me, the bloodline of the Zhan clan, won’t be encroached by its coldness.

128
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:54,160
Why is it you?

129
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:07,830
The sky changed.
(Sky also means the authority of a nation.)

130
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:20,530
How’s the king?

131
00:14:20,530 --> 00:14:23,130
I have done my best.

132
00:14:23,130 --> 00:14:24,740
Mister, you mean?

133
00:14:24,740 --> 00:14:28,750
Prime Minister! Prime Minister! Prime Minister!

134
00:14:31,610 --> 00:14:34,300
Mr. Zong isn’t a stranger. Speak up quickly.

135
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:37,430
- The king... The king—
- What happened to the king?

136
00:14:37,430 --> 00:14:40,180
They said the king has a glowing face and smooth breath right now.

137
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:43,410
It seems like his health has improved.

138
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:55,020
Healing and saving people are a healer’s job.

139
00:14:55,020 --> 00:14:58,000
I, Zong, have a clear conscience.

140
00:15:02,980 --> 00:15:08,260
Mr. Zong, why are you doing this?

141
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:13,110
For Prime Minister and myself.

142
00:15:13,110 --> 00:15:15,310
Who exactly are you?

143
00:15:15,310 --> 00:15:17,120
Ask her.

144
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:19,750
I don’t know him.

145
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:25,540
The little girl from Mt. Mystic Soul in the past has now become an excellent female fighter.

146
00:15:25,540 --> 00:15:28,470
Even I, your unfamiliar friend, am taking benefit from you.

147
00:15:28,470 --> 00:15:29,790
Am I right?

148
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:32,360
It seems like your injury wasn’t bad enough.

149
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:36,400
Your body did get well quite fast,

150
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:38,120
but I was hurt here.

151
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:40,260
It would not heal that fast.

152
00:15:42,190 --> 00:15:43,440
Why exactly are you here?

153
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,610
To save both of your lives.

154
00:15:45,610 --> 00:15:47,630
I don’t need you to save my life.

155
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:50,140
Your Highness Prince Fierce, you don't need to target me on everything.

156
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:54,170
Anyhow, we met once before.

157
00:15:54,170 --> 00:15:55,840
Who exactly are you?

158
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,910
You’ll know my real identity in the future.

159
00:15:57,910 --> 00:16:01,460
I would like to ask both of you to leave along with me immediately.

160
00:16:02,090 --> 00:16:04,220
I’m here to get my own thing.

161
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:05,700
What does it have to do with you?

162
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:08,070
Even though it’s your Zhan clan's treasure for thousands of years,

163
00:16:08,070 --> 00:16:10,120
you cannot touch it right now.

164
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:12,210
Then, let's give it a try.

165
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:17,170
Stop fighting.

166
00:16:18,170 --> 00:16:20,070
Do you worry about me?

167
00:16:20,070 --> 00:16:22,430
You should worry about yourself.

168
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:25,120
Zhan Beiye!

169
00:16:27,850 --> 00:16:29,840
Enough, both of you.

170
00:16:31,580 --> 00:16:34,140
I’m asking you. Why can’t we get it?

171
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:36,480
We are all in Qi Zhen’s trap now.

172
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,910
If you want to take the Earth Absorbing Bell now,

173
00:16:37,910 --> 00:16:40,880
everything in front of us, including you, me

174
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:44,100
and him, will become fragments of bone and blood.

175
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:11,590
Godfather, there’s news from the palace.

176
00:17:11,590 --> 00:17:14,820
The king has passed away.

177
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:20,690
I've done my best.

178
00:17:20,690 --> 00:17:22,860
The king’s health improved initially,

179
00:17:22,860 --> 00:17:24,770
but this is his fate.

180
00:17:24,770 --> 00:17:27,060
I can’t do anything, either.

181
00:17:32,170 --> 00:17:34,550
God!

182
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:42,490
Why do you treat our Deep Water like this?

183
00:17:44,890 --> 00:17:47,680
King!

184
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:50,550
I couldn’t share your burden.

185
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:54,020
I deserve to die!

186
00:17:59,030 --> 00:18:06,090
I’m afraid it won’t rain on the night of the red moon.

187
00:18:18,860 --> 00:18:20,630
Godfather.

188
00:18:21,410 --> 00:18:23,020
Godfather.

189
00:18:35,150 --> 00:18:39,590
We shall start. Right?

190
00:18:41,100 --> 00:18:43,240
How can you prove that what you said is the truth?

191
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:49,160
If you don’t believe me, you can use our lives as your bet and take the Earth Absorbing Bell away now.

192
00:18:50,670 --> 00:18:52,690
Then, when can we get it?

193
00:18:52,690 --> 00:18:55,640
According to what I know, once the Earth Absorbing Bell is used,

194
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:58,070
it will be connected to a person’s flesh, blood and spirit.

195
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:59,670
Right?

196
00:19:01,610 --> 00:19:04,070
- Yes.
- Just wait for three days then.

197
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:07,170
Within these three days, Qi Zhen will surely use this Earth Absorbing Bell.

198
00:19:07,170 --> 00:19:09,670
Once the Earth Absorbing Bell is used for other uses, Xiaoqi will be freed then.

199
00:19:09,670 --> 00:19:11,960
It won't be too late for you to rescue him then.

200
00:19:13,150 --> 00:19:15,660
How did you know about this?

201
00:19:15,660 --> 00:19:17,580
This is my business.

202
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:21,940
You just have to know, you can’t simply move the Earth Absorbing Bell.

203
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:24,240
This place is surrounded by the Prime Minister’s guards.

204
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:27,420
If you don’t leave now, the guards in the next shift will discover you soon.

205
00:19:29,090 --> 00:19:32,680
All right, I’ll trust you this time.

206
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:37,480
All right, you'll be in trouble if I find out that you’re lying.

207
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:39,350
Anytime.

208
00:19:43,940 --> 00:19:45,410
Let’s go.

209
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:31,960
On the day of the red moon, using the Earth Absorbing Bell as a token,

210
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:33,990
using the blood of Xuanyuan as a guide

211
00:20:33,990 --> 00:20:35,610
and sacrifices to the heavens and the earth,

212
00:20:35,610 --> 00:20:38,280
you can then master the Water Manipulation Technique

213
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:41,890
and be comparable to anyone of the Xuanyuan bloodline.

214
00:23:35,010 --> 00:23:42,150
From now on, Deep Water doesn’t need the Xuanyuan clan.

215
00:24:36,570 --> 00:24:40,290
[Prime Minister’s Manor]

216
00:25:32,580 --> 00:25:36,820
People say, “You can't get Deep Water’s Golden Scale Silk even by exchanging half of the town for it.”

217
00:25:36,820 --> 00:25:38,950
It's solely used to create the robe for the Emperor.

218
00:25:38,950 --> 00:25:41,940
I only believe when I personally witness this.

219
00:25:41,940 --> 00:25:45,770
Godfather’s wish will finally come true at Forever Water today.

220
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:54,220
It's finally the day.

221
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,650
Have the arrangements for Deep Water been completed?

222
00:25:58,650 --> 00:26:01,840
Based on your instructions, we have assigned special people to guard the water curtains and watercourses.

223
00:26:01,840 --> 00:26:04,360
I have bribed a few main officials.

224
00:26:04,360 --> 00:26:06,470
Godfather, don’t be worried.

225
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:15,260
Remember, our hard work over half of our lives depends on today.

226
00:26:15,260 --> 00:26:19,110
But, Godfather, what should we do with the Earth Absorbing Bell?

227
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:24,410
How can we simply pass this treasure, Earth Absorbing Bell, to the others?

228
00:26:24,410 --> 00:26:26,790
Have it fed on the kid we just caught previously.

229
00:26:26,790 --> 00:26:30,380
It will definitely be of use someday.

230
00:26:30,380 --> 00:26:31,890
Yes.

231
00:27:42,280 --> 00:27:46,540
As soon as the king is dead, the reservoir in Forever Water is opened.

232
00:27:46,540 --> 00:27:49,220
If we let the water keep running freely,

233
00:27:49,220 --> 00:27:52,440
it will be a drowning disaster for Deep Water.

234
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:56,140
Marquis , please quickly let the Heir Apparent take over the throne and manipulate the water.

235
00:27:56,140 --> 00:27:58,770
Isn't the Heir Apparent here?

236
00:27:58,770 --> 00:28:01,460
Today’s the funeral of the deceased king of Deep Water.

237
00:28:01,460 --> 00:28:04,970
Who can manipulate the water if the Heir Apparent isn’t here?

238
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:37,520
[Widely Spread Kindness and Grace]

239
00:28:49,220 --> 00:28:52,130
Long live the King.

240
00:28:53,510 --> 00:28:56,420
Long live the King.

241
00:29:13,690 --> 00:29:17,380
Godfather, I just heard that they found a young man in the south of the city.

242
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:19,400
That man is Xuanyuan Min.

243
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:22,220
There was no news about him after he appeared in the slave market.

244
00:29:22,220 --> 00:29:24,520
He suddenly appears now.

245
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:27,510
I’m afraid that there may be something behind him.

246
00:29:27,510 --> 00:29:29,580
Godfather, are you saying that—

247
00:29:29,580 --> 00:29:32,250
Don’t be afraid. Things have become like this.

248
00:29:32,250 --> 00:29:35,380
Even if he has a scheme,

249
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:37,830
I'm afraid it will be just a fantasy.

250
00:29:37,830 --> 00:29:41,110
You go find people to get rid of him.

251
00:29:41,110 --> 00:29:42,060
Yes.

252
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:43,710
Wait a minute.

253
00:29:46,110 --> 00:29:47,350
Go there personally.

254
00:29:47,350 --> 00:29:51,400
Remember, I need to see his corpse if he dies.

255
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:52,880
Yes.

